response.overview: On September 1st GCW: Say You Will 2023 is live on FITE+ straight from Grand Sports Arena in Hoffman Estates, IL. The event features GCW World Title Match where Blake Christian defends his title against Francesco Akira.  Also in the lineup:  Lash LeRoux vs Joey Janela  Tag Team Match Violence Is Forever (Dominic Garrini & Kevin Ku) vs BUSSY (Allie Katch & Effy)  Tag Team Match Masha Slamovich & Rina Yamashita vs Los Macizos (Ciclope & Miedo Extremo)  Nick Gage vs El Hijo del Vikingo
response.title: GCW Say You Will 2023
